
Privacy Policy
Last updated: July 16, 2025
This app (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. Please read the following to learn how we handle your data.
1. Information We Collect
Device ID: Collected for analytics, third-party advertising (such as Google AdMob), and tracking purposes.
Advertising Data: Collected for analytics, third-party advertising, and tracking purposes.
Crash Data: Collected for app functionality and analytics.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the above data to improve app performance, provide personalized ads, analyze usage, and ensure app stability.
Third-party services (such as Google AdMob) may collect and use your data for advertising and analytics. For details, please refer to Google AdMob Privacy Policy.
3. Data Sharing
We do not sell or share your personal information with any other third parties except as required for third-party advertising and analytics.
4. Data Security
We do not store any user data on our own servers. All data is processed by third-party services or remains on your device.
5. Children’s Privacy
Our app does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13.
6. Changes to This Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at: tln61806088@email.com
隐私政策
最后更新日期：2025年7月16日
本应用（“我们”）尊重您的隐私，并致力于保护您的个人信息。请阅读以下内容，了解我们如何处理您的数据。
1. 我们收集的信息
设备ID：用于分析、第三方广告（如Google AdMob）和追踪目的。
广告数据：用于分析、第三方广告和追踪目的。
崩溃数据：用于App功能和分析。
2. 我们如何使用您的信息
我们使用上述数据以提升应用性能、提供个性化广告、分析使用情况并确保应用稳定性。
第三方服务（如Google AdMob）可能会收集和使用您的数据用于广告和分析。详情请参阅 Google AdMob 隐私政策。
3. 数据共享
除第三方广告和分析所需外，我们不会向其他第三方出售或分享您的个人信息。
4. 数据安全
我们不会在自有服务器上存储任何用户数据。所有数据均由第三方服务处理或保留在您的设备上。
5. 儿童隐私
我们不会有意收集13岁以下儿童的任何信息。
6. 政策变更
我们可能会不时更新本隐私政策。任何更改都会在本页面公布。
7. 联系我们
如对本隐私政策有任何疑问或建议，请联系：tln61806088@gmail.com
